{
  "description": "A low-angle view captures a massive port crane against a clear, bright blue sky. The crane is primarily white with a complex network of steel beams and supporting structures.  Numerous lights are attached along the crane\u2019s arm, likely for nighttime operations. A small cabin or control room is suspended from the crane, appearing as a dark rectangle.  The words 'PORT OF OAKLAND' are prominently displayed in bold black lettering on the crane's structure. Several thin, vertical cables extend downwards from the crane. A portion of another crane structure is visible on the left side of the frame. ",
